title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 720-3.4 - Numbering of leaves
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 720-3.4 - Numbering of leaves

State Regulations

Numbering of leaves shall follow a format specified in
the Department of Public Service's Electronic Tariff System: Utility Preparer's

Guide (See Appendix 7-H of this Title). Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16
§§
720-3.4

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
